<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>计算机 on 贤民的博客</title><link>https://www.xianmin.org/categories/%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E6%9C%BA/</link><description>Recent content in 计算机 on 贤民的博客</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>zh-cn</language><lastBuildDate>Fri, 20 Sep 2024 11:46:43 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://www.xianmin.org/categories/%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E6%9C%BA/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>博客主题 Jane V3 大版本更新</title><link>https://www.xianmin.org/post/2024/2024-09-20-jane-theme-v3-major-update/</link><pubDate>Fri, 20 Sep 2024 11:29:47 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.xianmin.org/post/2024/2024-09-20-jane-theme-v3-major-update/</guid><description>&lt;p>项目主页： &lt;a href="https://github.com/xianmin/hugo-theme-jane">https://github.com/xianmin/hugo-theme-jane&lt;/a> 。&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="更新内容">更新内容&lt;/h2>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>使用 &lt;a href="https://picocss.com/">Pico CSS&lt;/a> 作为配色方案，可切换主题颜色，可切换 dark / light 模式。&lt;/li>
